	   <tr><td colspan=2>does anyone know if having spell haste ii on more than one item stacks at all?&nbsp;&nbsp;or is it the same?<br>&nbsp;<br>Yelsraek Alongirical<br>51st Dark Elf Wizard<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=117596" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=117596</a><br><br>Arabesque Hightorch<br>40th Human Cleric<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=178883" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=178883</a><br>DRo</td></tr>
